Chapter 14: Frog Level

Mirror was never meant to be something so... alive. In the quiet aftermath of my death and rebirth, the world had become a different place. The skinwalker had left its mark, a scar across the landscape and my very existence. Everything felt wrong, distorted, twisted under its influence. But the strangest thing about it all? I could feel something new bubbling up beneath the surface, something I hadn‚Äôt anticipated.

