Chapter 24: Tower Defense

The peace that had settled over Mirror after the successful implementation of the LBRO was short-lived. While the skinwalkers were certainly kept at bay by the octagonal barrier, I knew they wouldn‚Äôt give up easily. They had tried to infiltrate before, and now that they had tasted the frustration of being blocked, I could sense their growing desire to break through.

