That‚Äôs when the idea struck me.

Tower Defense.

Step 1: Building the Foundation

I wasn‚Äôt new to constructing things in Mirror. After all, this was my world, my creation. I could shape the land however I wanted, create structures and systems that served my needs. The LBRO had been a step in the right direction, but it was a passive defense, something that kept the skinwalkers from crossing into my domain. Now, I needed to build an active defense system.

