Once the towers were completed, it was time for the true test. I had no doubt that the design would work‚Äîthe real question was whether the towers could function as a unified defense system. Could they work together? Could they stop the skinwalkers if they decided to test their new strategy?

I stood at the center of my domain, watching as the towers came to life. The first one activated with a low hum, its core glowing bright as the energy surged through its network. The others followed, their lights blinking on one by one, creating a web of power that enveloped the entire region.

