Step 4: Midday Reflections and Social Connections

By midday, the heat of the sun began to settle over Mirror. The world was bustling with life‚Äîthe animals, the plants, the elements‚Äîeverything was alive, moving in sync with the rhythms of time. This was the time when I would often pause and connect with the other beings who shared Mirror with me.

