Step 1: The Titan Lobster

The first Titan we encountered was the Titan Lobster, a creature whose size alone was enough to send ripples through Mirror‚Äôs oceans. Unlike its smaller counterparts, the Titan Lobster was a creature of unimaginable scale and strength, its massive claws capable of tearing through entire structures with ease. But there was more to this beast than brute force. The Titan Lobster represented the unrelenting power of the sea‚Äîits ability to shape and reshape the world around it through the forces of the ocean.

