Chapter 68: Yarn Portals

It had been days since we first discovered the Magic Yarn, and with each passing moment, the strange object seemed to hold more and more significance. Aemily and I had become fully immersed in its playful yet profound power, exploring its ability to shape reality and create connections between worlds. What had started as a simple game of Cat's Cradle had turned into something far more powerful‚Äîa gateway to the unknown.

