Step 3: Mita‚Äôs Purpose

I had to know more. I needed to understand her purpose, what she meant for the world I had created and for me.

‚ÄúWhat do you want?‚Äù I asked, my voice quiet but filled with curiosity. ‚ÄúWhat is your purpose?‚Äù

