Step 5: The Decision to Move Forward

As the sun began to set, casting a golden light over the water, I felt a sense of peace settle within me. The North Sea had been a revelation‚Äîa reminder of how much there was to discover, both in the world and within myself. The sea was vast and untamed, but it was also full of potential, a place where anything was possible.

