Chapter 91: Night 8: Doppelvier Nightmare: PTSD Trauma

The moment I closed my eyes, the world around me began to shift again, this time not in the familiar fluidity of a dreamscape, but in the jagged edges of something far darker. I knew, instinctively, that this wasn‚Äôt going to be like the dreams before. Something was different, something more sinister was lurking just below the surface.

