‚ÄúI am the President,‚Äù it said again, its voice now both mine and not mine, reverberating through the city, ‚Äúand this city, this world, is mine to control. You, Mira, have come to the heart of the Skinwalkers‚Äô domain. You belong to me now.‚Äù

